column2:
To help us track individual responses and maintain anonymity in this section, please provide a unique code below. The unique code should include:
The last two digits of the year you started going to UC Berkeley (e.g., 22 if you transferred to UC Berkeley in 2022)
Your middle initial or the last letter of your first name if you do not have a middle name (e.g. M if your name is Apple Mango Orange)
The day of your birthday (e.g. 11 if you were born on May 11, 2002)
First three letters of the city where you were born (e.g., HER if you were born in Hercules)
For example: 22-M-11-HER
